{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-jsx","path":"/react/scheduler/docs/guides/appointment-tooltip/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"react-scheduler---appointment-tooltip\"><a href=\"#react-scheduler---appointment-tooltip\" aria-label=\"react scheduler   appointment tooltip permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>React Scheduler - Appointment Tooltip</h1>\n<p>An appointment tooltip displays information about the appointment and contains buttons that manage the appointment.</p>\n<h2 id=\"related-plugins\"><a href=\"#related-plugins\" aria-label=\"related plugins permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Related Plugins</h2>\n<p>The following plugin is required:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"../reference/appointment-tooltip.md\">AppointmentTooltip</a> - displays the appointment tooltip</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"basic-usage\"><a href=\"#basic-usage\" aria-label=\"basic usage permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Basic Usage</h2>\n<p>Import the plugin listed above. A user can click on an appointment to show its tooltip.</p>\n<h3 id=\"uncontrolled-mode\"><a href=\"#uncontrolled-mode\" aria-label=\"uncontrolled mode permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Uncontrolled Mode</h3>\n<p>The following demo shows how to use the appointment tooltip in uncontrolled mode:</p>\n<p>.embedded-demo({ \"path\": \"scheduler-tooltip/uncontrolled\", \"showThemeSelector\": true })</p>\n<h3 id=\"controlled-mode\"><a href=\"#controlled-mode\" aria-label=\"controlled mode permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Controlled Mode</h3>\n<p>In controlled mode, the state of <code class=\"language-text\">AppointmentTooltip</code>s should be controlled externally. To control their visibility, pass the <code class=\"language-text\">visible</code> property and <code class=\"language-text\">onVisibilityChange</code> event to the plugin. To manage the displayed data, pass the <a href=\"../reference/appointment-tooltip.md#appointmentmeta\">appointmentMeta</a> property and <code class=\"language-text\">onAppointmentMetaChange</code> event.</p>\n<p>.embedded-demo({ \"path\": \"scheduler-tooltip/controlled\", \"showThemeSelector\": true })</p>\n<h3 id=\"customize-the-appearance\"><a href=\"#customize-the-appearance\" aria-label=\"customize the appearance permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Customize the Appearance</h3>\n<p>To customize the tooltip's appearance, specify the <code class=\"language-text\">xxxComponent</code> properties (<code class=\"language-text\">xxx</code> is the name of the element you want to customize). For example, the <code class=\"language-text\">headerComponent</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">contentComponent</code> properties are used to customize the tooltip's header and content, as shown in the code below. Refer to the <a href=\"../reference/appointment-tooltip.md\">AppointmentTooltip API reference page</a> for a list of all <code class=\"language-text\">xxxComponent</code> properties.</p>\n<p>.embedded-demo({ \"path\": \"scheduler-tooltip/custom\", \"showThemeSelector\": true })</p>","fields":{"technology":"react/scheduler","section":"docs"},"frontmatter":{"title":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"react/scheduler/docs/guides/appointment-tooltip/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216","3662068265"]}